title: Mid laner looking for a fun Clash team :')
body:
Heyo just moved to Australia so I haven't done any real ranked here besides my placements. On NA I am plat but I really don't mind playing with any rank as long as its not above plat aha. My id is "Im fkin trash" so add me up if you wanna have me on your team. I main assassins for the most part although i have picks for almost every role in the mid lane. 

Hit me up!

replies.body: hey I'll join i'm an aatrox main
